item.title: Meetup - Tuesday 17th May 2016 at The ODI Node in Leeds
item.description: No sooner is one LeedsDevops at an end than another turns up, so all aboard for our next Devops meetup. Join us at The ODI Node in Leeds on Tuesday 17th May 2016 for an exciting evening of devops talks: 6:45 - 7:15 : Grab a beer, have a natter. 7:15 - 7:30 : Group updates/news/announcements 7:30 - 8:00 : Rob Tuley - Sky Betting and Gaming 8:00 - 8:15 : Intermission
